      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm just really scared of a hypoglycemic episode while i'm sleeping. wouldn't it be more logical to just skip it this one time since i barely ate anything? it's just a small adjustment, surely it won't hurt to miss one night if my sugar is already stable.",
